description: The Lafitte Greenway, a major part of the Lafitte Greenway Corridor, is a 3.1-mile long strip of land bounded by Basin Street, Lafitte Avenue, N. Jefferson Davis Parkway, and St. Louis Street and including the entire St. Louis Street right-of-way between N. Jefferson Davis Parkway and Canal Boulevard. http://lafittecorridorconnection.com/
